snippet.title: Warp Rider Trailer
snippet.description: Warp Rider! New arcade intense action is here! Dodge and shoot through 30 crazy levels. Difficult obstacles, randomized pitfalls, and shooting sentry guns will keep you on the edge of your seat. Choose from different difficulty settings and put yourself to the ultimate challenge. Enjoy wicked visuals, fast paced action, and easy controls when you play Warp Rider!
